{"product_id":"navy-basic-bottom","title":"NAVY BASIC BOTTOM","description":"\u003cp\u003e MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32 WEARING M BOTTOMS.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n420 GSM TAPED COTTON FLEECE\u003cbr\u003e\nCOMBED \u0026amp; BIO-WASHED FINISH\u003cbr\u003e\nSTRAIGHT BAGGY FIT\u003cbr\u003e\nNAVY BLUE MINIMAL DESIGN\u003cbr\u003e\nUNISEX ARTICLE [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS]. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCrafted from 420 GSM premium taped cotton fleece for a structured, soft feel with long-lasting durability.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStraight baggy silhouette ensures relaxed comfort with a clean streetwear profile.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMinimal blank design allows effortless pairing with both bold graphics and everyday basics.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeep navy blue tone offers a refined alternative to black while remaining timeless and versatile.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTaped fleece construction enhances structure without restricting movement.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePerfect for all seasons, delivering warmth, breathability, and a premium heavyweight finish.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMachine wash the bottoms inside out with similar colors.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse cold water to maintain fabric texture and color richness.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to preserve shape.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStore folded in a cool, dry place to retain structure and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e420 GSM taped fleece for a dense, premium feel.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStraight baggy fit for versatile comfort and styling.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnisex silhouette suited for a wide range of body types.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMinimal blank aesthetic for easy outfit pairing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eElasticated waist for adjustable everyday comfort.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBalanced fabric weight suitable for year-round wear.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46885005590682,"sku":"DS SIGNATURE SWEATPANTS","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885005623450,"sku":"DS SIGNATURE SWEATPANTS","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46885005656218,"sku":"DS SIGNATURE SWEATPANTS","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885005688986,"sku":"DS SIGNATURE SWEATPANTS","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46885005721754,"sku":"DS SIGNATURE SWEATPANTS","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885005754522,"sku":"DS SIGNATURE SWEATPANTS","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/IMG_5631_11zon_1.webp?v=1772291602","url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/products\/navy-basic-bottom","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}